festival.introText:
The UK's maddest small festival. Featuring the best in underground sounds from DnB to tekno, punk to reggae and everything good in between!

 

Full line-up release in January.

 

Balter - 'To dance clumsily, without particular grace or skill, but usually with great enjoyment'

 

Header image: Jack Kimber Photography

reviews.title: Review of Balter Festival
reviews.body: Sick music and awesome people. Think it may have been the best weekend ever :D

location.address: Chepstow Racecourse, St Lawrence Road, SN14

news.title: Balter Festival 2023: Tickets on sale this Wednesday - sign up now
news.summary: Returning to Chepstow Racecourse in Wales next year, the UK's 'maddest' small festival will provide an eclectic programme of live music across one long sunny weekend in May
